[normal]a multi agency process of identification of girls affected by gangs, identifying risk and developing pathways to enable appropriate support
[normal], together with work to o
[normal]ffer early intervention support to girls involved in gangs.
[normal] There is also a Report being produced for the Cha
[normal]i
[normal]rs of Strategic Partnerships Meeting for the 26 November to outline the National Response to 
