[normal]A[bold]PCP C1.7 Improve BME experience of policing through better engagement and being more responsive to needs.
[normal]Following a commissioned research project, the Commissioner has approved the review and implementation of the x30 recommendations and report back to the BME Project Steering Group. 
[normal]A
[normal] Joint Working Group 
[normal]has been 
